  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/64bf0593a063488abd8424bcfc79bb48.poster.avif?t=1734357995\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/64bf0593a063488abd8424bcfc79bb48.webm?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/64bf0593a063488abd8424bcfc79bb48.mp4?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/9a41528fca545c315f41084712a4542e.poster.avif?t=1734357995\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/9a41528fca545c315f41084712a4542e.webm?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/9a41528fca545c315f41084712a4542e.mp4?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Let's Roll</strong></h2>This is a game where you become a pirate and overcome obstacles. <br>If you work hard, you will reach your goal.<br>It is a third-person platformer genre.<br>There is no set save point but you can save using skill.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls</strong></h2>Move - w,a,s,d<br>Jump - space<br>Attack - mouse left click<br>Time delay, Aim - mouse right click<br>Skill - E,R<br>Option - Esc<br>Crouch - Alt<br>Sprint - Shift<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tips</strong></h2>Don't Fall into the Sea<br>If the game is difficult, collect a lot of coins<br>If you press alt right before falling, you will roll forward<br>Do not try to climb on moving objects<br>The gun fires only when aiming<br>Please enjoy the game~",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/64bf0593a063488abd8424bcfc79bb48.poster.avif?t=1734357995\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/64bf0593a063488abd8424bcfc79bb48.webm?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/64bf0593a063488abd8424bcfc79bb48.mp4?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/9a41528fca545c315f41084712a4542e.poster.avif?t=1734357995\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/9a41528fca545c315f41084712a4542e.webm?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817240/extras/9a41528fca545c315f41084712a4542e.mp4?t=1734357995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Let's Roll</strong></h2>This is a game where you become a pirate and overcome obstacles. <br>If you work hard, you will reach your goal.<br>It is a third-person platformer genre.<br>There is no set save point but you can save using skill.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls</strong></h2>Move - w,a,s,d<br>Jump - space<br>Attack - mouse left click<br>Time delay, Aim - mouse right click<br>Skill - E,R<br>Option - Esc<br>Crouch - Alt<br>Sprint - Shift<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tips</strong></h2>Don't Fall into the Sea<br>If the game is difficult, collect a lot of coins<br>If you press alt right before falling, you will roll forward<br>Do not try to climb on moving objects<br>The gun fires only when aiming<br>Please enjoy the game~",
